1. the owner of the goat is not to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##8
2. the person driving the car is the person driving the car##1
3. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the doctor##5
4. the person driving the car is not to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##8
5. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the left of the owner of the pony##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
| Pet        | goat | pony            |
| Hobby       | writing | chess              |
| Job         | doctor  | software-developer |
| Transport   | car     | snowmobile         |

